Cloudflare Worker scaffold written: router + 8 endpoints, wrangler.toml with 4 KV namespaces, wg-cache.js hybrid sync.
Files written: worker/worker.js, worker/wrangler.toml; file edited: js/core/wg-cache.js.
8 endpoints (save, load, iap-grant, account-upgrade, event, duel-match, duel-result, leaderboard) + 4 KV namespaces (WG_STATE, WG_IAP, WG_ACCOUNT, WG_EVENTS).
